<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>COVID-19 UK Vaccination Tracker</title>
        <link
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400&display=swap"
            rel="stylesheet">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
        <link rel="icon" href="/img/favicon.png" type="image/png" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <main>
            <h1>COVID-19 Vaccinations Administered in the UK</h1>
            <span id="vaccine-count">$vaccinationsFormatted</span><br />
            <span id="vaccine-diff">($vaccinationsDiffFormatted)</span>
        </main>
        <footer>
          Figures as released by the UK government on $dataFromDateFormatted (figures released daily). Difference amount shown is the amount changed in total vaccinations between $dataFromDateMinus1Formatted and $dataFromDateFormatted. Note: this data includes total vaccinations, not people vaccinated. $firstDoseFormatted people have been given their first dose, and $secondDoseFormatted their second dose.<p />
          <strong>last updated $lastCheckFormatted</strong>
        </footer>
        <script src="js/script.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>